# This directory is for model files.
# Models are not included in git but are bundled when you run pip install.
#
# To set up:
# 1. Download RealESRGAN_x4plus.pth from:
#    https://github.com/xinntao/Real-ESRGAN/releases/download/v0.1.0/RealESRGAN_x4plus.pth
#
# 2. On Mac, convert to CoreML:
#    python scripts/setup_model.py
#
# 3. Install the package:
#    pip install .
#
# The model will be bundled and auto-detected.
